<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="883" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="10.[212,1172,490,937]" box="[212,310,490,514]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">
<heading box="[212,310,490,514]" fontSize="10" level="3" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" reason="5">
<emphasis box="[212,310,490,514]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[212,1172,490,937]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Mello-Leitao" baseAuthorityYear="1923" box="[212,443,530,554]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exilis">
<emphasis box="[212,443,530,554]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Hapalotremus exilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by a single female from Campina Grande (
<collectingRegion box="[219,308,561,585]" country="Brazil" name="Paraiba" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Paraíba</collectingRegion>
) (
<figureCitation box="[337,437,561,585]" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="7.[144,211,835,857]" captionTargetBox="[144,1104,168,803]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[144,1104,168,804]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figure 4. Distribution map of Hapalotremus species in South America." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4004670" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4004670/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Figure 4</figureCitation>
) and the 
<typeStatus box="[559,607,562,586]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">type</typeStatus>
material has been listed as ‘not located’ in the annotated check list by 
<bibRefCitation author="Silva-Moreira TD &amp; Baptista RLC &amp; Kury AB &amp; Giupponi APL &amp; Buckup EH &amp; Brescovit AD" box="[502,817,593,617]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" pagination="1 - 91" refId="ref7252" refString="Silva-Moreira TD, Baptista RLC, Kury AB, Giupponi APL, Buckup EH, Brescovit AD. 2010. Annotated check list of Arachnida type specimens deposited in the Museu Nacional, Rio de Janeiro. II- Araneae. Zootaxa. 2588: 1 - 91." type="journal article" year="2010">Silva-Moreira et al. (2010)</bibRefCitation>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[865,984,593,617]" class="Arachnida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="class">Arachnida</taxonomicName>
<typeStatus box="[998,1046,594,618]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">type</typeStatus>
specimens deposited in the Museu Nacional, 
<collectingRegion box="[622,800,625,649]" country="Brazil" name="Rio de Janeiro" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Rio de Janeiro</collectingRegion>
. According to the geographical distribution and many of the morphological characteristics from the original description, such as the small size of the female and the reduced number of labial and maxillary cuspules, together with the shape of the spermathecae presented by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bucherl W &amp; Da Costa TA &amp; Lucas S" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" pagination="117 - 138" refId="ref5944" refString="Bucherl W, Da Costa TA, Lucas S. 1971. Revisao de alguns tipos de Aranhas caranguejeiras (Orthognatha) establecidos por Candido de Mello-Leitao e depositados no Museu Nacional do Rio. Mem Inst Butantan. 35: 117 - 138." type="journal article" year="1971">Bücherl et al. (1971)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Schmidt G" box="[433,612,753,777]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" pagination="16 - 18" refId="ref7201" refString="Schmidt G. 2002. Dolichothele ist kein Synonym von Haplotremus (Araneae: Theraphosidae: Theraphosinae). Tarantulas of the World. 7: 16 - 18." type="journal article" year="2002">Schmidt (2002)</bibRefCitation>
it could be a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Guadanucci 2011)" baseAuthorityName="Guadanucci" baseAuthorityYear="2011" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Oligoxystre" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1042,1171,753,777]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Oligoxystre</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Guadanucci JPL" box="[219,434,785,809]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" pagination="320 - 326" refId="ref6282" refString="Guadanucci JPL. 2011. Cladistic analysis and biogeography of the genus Oligoxystre Vellard 1924 (Araneae: Mygalomorphae: Theraphosidae). J Arachnol. 39: 320 - 326. doi: 10.1636 / CA 10 - 81.1" type="journal article" year="2011">Guadanucci 2011</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
or 
<emphasis box="[517,615,785,809]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">Guruyita</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Guadanucci JPL &amp; Lucas SM &amp; Indicatti RP &amp; Yamamoto FU" box="[647,959,785,809]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" pagination="991 - 996" refId="ref6322" refString="Guadanucci JPL, Lucas SM, Indicatti RP, Yamamoto FU. 2007. Description of Guyruita gen. nov. and two new species (Ischnocolinae, Theraphosidae). Rev Bras Zool. 24: 991 - 996. doi: 10.1590 / S 0101 - 81752007000400015" type="journal article" year="2007">Guadanucci et al. 2007</bibRefCitation>
) (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1892" box="[1000,1160,785,809]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Ischnocolinae">Ischnocolinae</taxonomicName>
). Unfortunately, the original description does not warrant recognition of the species, and, therefore the identity of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Mello-Leitao" baseAuthorityYear="1923" box="[571,670,849,873]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="883" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exilis">
<emphasis box="[571,670,849,873]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">H. exilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
cannot be confirmed. The species is here considered 
<emphasis box="[340,539,880,904]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">species inquirenda</emphasis>
, pending the finding of the 
<typeStatus box="[856,904,881,905]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">type</typeStatus>
material or availability and careful examination of material from the 
<typeStatus box="[738,786,913,937]" pageId="10" pageNumber="883">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
